PN,42301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA police officer who hit and killed a
OL,8,F74-year-old motorbike passenger after
OL,9,Fspeeding through a red light while
OL,10,Fresponding to a 999 call has been
OL,11,Fjailed despite the victim's family
OL,12,Fsaying they "did not want him to go to
OL,13,Fprison for doing his job".
OL,15,FPC Mark Roberts was answering a grade-
OL,16,Fone emergency call about a choking
OL,17,Fbaby when he went through a red light
OL,18,Fwhich had been on 'stop' for six
OL,19,Fseconds and collided with Ronald and
OL,20,FMuriel Pinkney in his marked
OL,21,FNorthumbria Police car.
OL,26,@tD@MOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FMrs Pinkney suffered fatal head and
OL,8,Fneck injuries in the crash on a 30mph
OL,9,Fstretch of road near the Metrocentre
OL,10,Fin Gateshead in July 2022.
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct (IOPC) said PC Roberts was
OL,14,Fdriving at 43mph as he approached the
OL,15,Flights and was still going at around
OL,16,F25mph when his vehicle collided with
OL,17,Fthe couple.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe 57-year-old officer, who lives in
OL,8,FDarlington, was found guilty of
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving. He
OL,10,Fwas also convicted of causing Mr
OL,11,FPinkney, who suffered a bleed on the
OL,12,Fbrain and multiple fractures, serious
OL,13,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,15,FThe prosecution said Roberts should
OL,16,Fhave approached the junction more
OL,17,Fslowly and told the jury the police's
OL,18,Fdriving guidance stated that risk
OL,19,Ftaking, even in a "noble cause", was
OL,20,Fnot justified.
OL,26,@{D@SOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA statement from the couple's
OL,8,Fdaughter, Dawn Hunter-Pinkney, said
OL,9,Fthe family "don't blame the officer
OL,10,Ffor what happened".
OL,12,F"For a long time we were angry but the
OL,13,Fmore we hear about why the officer was
OL,14,Fdriving the way he was, the more we
OL,15,Funderstand," she said.
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@RO]tD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe victim impact statement, read
OL,8,Fduring the sentencing hearing at
OL,9,FTeesside Crown Court on Tuesday, went
OL,10,Fon to say: "We don't want him to go to
OL,11,Fprison for doing his job. We do accept
OL,12,Fthis is a very tragic accident with a
OL,13,Fvery tragic outcome, but sending the
OL,14,Fofficer to prison won't bring mam
OL,15,Fback."
OL,17,FMs Hunter-Pinkney said her parents had
OL,18,Fbeen inseparable and her father had
OL,19,Fbeen devastated by his wife's death,
OL,20,Fgoing from doing everything with her
OL,21,Fto "doing almost nothing".
OL,26,@rD@LOUwD@FO]}D@DOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FIn mitigation, the court heard Roberts
OL,8,Fwas "heartbroken" by the accident and
OL,9,Fhad led a "remarkable life of public
OL,10,Fservice," joining the police after an
OL,11,FArmy career that saw him serve in
OL,12,FYugoslavia, Afghanistan and Iraq.
OL,14,FBut Judge Francis Laird KC, the
OL,15,FRecorder of Middlesbrough, jailed
OL,16,FRoberts for 27 months, saying: "In my
OL,17,Fjudgement only a custodial sentence
OL,18,Fcan be justified for these offences."
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@QO]qD@KOUrD@IO]xD@`OUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe judge told Roberts that as a
OL,8,Fpolice officer he was entitled to use
OL,9,Fexemptions from the speed limit and
OL,10,Fthe ban on driving through red lights,
OL,11,Fbut that "these exemptions must be
OL,12,Fexercised cautiously and
OL,13,Fappropriately".
OL,26,@sD@JOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FJudge Laird said: "Your speed as you
OL,8,Fapproached the junction was too high.
OL,9,F"You observed the junction was clear
OL,10,Fand you simply chose to drive through
OL,11,Fwithout stopping or at least reducing
OL,12,Fyour speed to a point where you could
OL,13,Fstop should another motorist enter the
OL,14,Fjunction."
OL,16,FHe went on to say: "The evidence
OL,17,Fsuggests Ronald and Muriel Pinkney
OL,18,Fwere visible to you when you
OL,19,Fapproached the junction, however you
OL,20,Fwere so focused on getting to your
OL,21,Fdestination you failed to notice them."
OL,26,@oD@SOUqD@AOUvD@JO]xD@TOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FRoberts was also banned from driving
OL,8,Ffor five years and one month, and must
OL,9,Fpass an extended retest to get his
OL,10,Flicence back. Roberts, who has been
OL,11,Fsuspended by his force, was arrested
OL,12,Fafter the collision and later answered
OL,13,F"no comment" to questions during his
OL,14,Fformal interview but provided a
OL,15,Fprepared statement.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FIn it, he said the ambulance service
OL,8,Fhad requested assistance about a
OL,9,Fchoking five-week-old baby, which
OL,10,Findicated paramedics did not believe
OL,11,Fthey could get to the patient before
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FRoberts said he took his marked
OL,15,Fvehicle from Whickham police station,
OL,16,Factivated his blue lights and sirens,
OL,17,Fchanging the tone of the alert at
OL,18,Ftimes, as he made his way through
OL,19,Ftraffic and red lights.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
