FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FMoments before the collision with the
OL,13,FPinkneys' motorbike, the officer saw a
OL,14,Fwhite van make an emergency stop, he
OL,15,Fsaid."I couldn't see anything else
OL,16,Fbefore travelling towards the
OL,17,Fjunction," the officer said in his
OL,18,Fstatement, which was read out in court
OL,19,Fon Tuesday.
OL,26,@wD@FOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"The next thing I recall is there was
OL,8,Fa bang and both airbags deployed and I
OL,9,Fhit the windscreen, which knocked me
OL,10,Fout for a few seconds."
OL,12,FHe then saw two people on the ground
OL,13,Fwith crash helmets on. He blacked out
OL,14,Fagain and was treated in an ambulance
OL,15,Fand then taken to hospital.
OL,17,FRoberts said: "I believe this was a
OL,18,Ftragic accident."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@WO]yD@OOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police, Andy Hill, said:
OL,9,F"Today, I reiterate my previous
OL,10,Fcomments in recognising that no words
OL,11,Fwill make the pain of Mr Pinkney, his
OL,12,Ffamily and anyone impacted by this
OL,13,Ftragic incident, any easier.
OL,15,F"On behalf of Northumbria Police, I
OL,16,Fwish to express my sincere condolences
OL,17,Ffor your loss and our thoughts very
OL,18,Fmuch continue to be with you at this
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"I also want to recognise the dignity
OL,8,Fthe family have shown throughout the
OL,9,Fproceedings.
OL,11,F"As is standard practice, this
OL,12,Fincident was referred to the
OL,13,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,14,F(IOPC) who carried out an
OL,15,Finvestigation and referred a file to
OL,16,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,17,Ffor consideration of criminal charges.
OL,19,F"Each and every day we respond to
OL,20,Femergencies and thankfully tragedies
OL,21,Fof this nature are extremely rare.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1775751065
OL,3,CPolice officer who caused fatal crash
OL,4,Cwhile responding to emergency call
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"Officers are highly-trained and
OL,8,Fsupported to help ensure they keep
OL,9,Fboth themselves and the public safe.
OL,11,F"Regrettably, on this occasion the
OL,12,Fstandard of driving fell short of what
OL,13,Fit is expected which has led to the
OL,14,Fmost devastating of outcomes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/15
